    <string name="disclosure_location_fine_title">GPS location access</string>
    <string name="disclosure_location_fine_body">geoHELP collects your device GPS location to include it in HELP requests and MAN DOWN emergency SMS sent to configured SOS numbers.\n\nData is not sold or used for ads. It is used only for rescue features you request.\n\nOn the next screen you can allow location access.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_location_background_title">Location when screen is off</string>
    <string name="disclosure_location_background_body">For MAN DOWN, geoHELP may use GPS while the screen is off during an alert, to send updated coordinates by SMS to emergency numbers.\n\nLocation data is not sold or shared with third parties for marketing: it is included only in emergency SMS to SOS recipients.\n\nOn the next screen choose “Allow all the time” (or equivalent).</string>
    <string name="disclosure_sms_title">Emergency SMS</string>
    <string name="disclosure_sms_body">geoHELP sends automatic SMS only during a MAN DOWN alert (after impact/fall and a cancellable countdown) to primary and backup SOS numbers configured for the service.\n\nThe message may include GPS location, name, birth year, phone and medical summary if you consented.\n\nData is not sold. On the next screen you can allow SMS from your device.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_notifications_title">MAN DOWN notifications</string>
    <string name="disclosure_notifications_body">geoHELP shows visible notifications during MAN DOWN: active service, countdown before SMS send, and alert status. You can cancel from the notification or in the app.\n\nOn the next screen you can allow notifications.</string>
